source.name: New Residential Construction
source.description: New Residential Construction provides national and regional data on the number of new housing units authorized by building permits; authorized, but not started; started; under construction; and completed. The data are for new, privately-owned housing units, excluding "HUD-code" manufactured (mobile) homes. The data are from the Building Permit Survey, and from the Survey of Construction (SOC), which is partially funded by the Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD).
